      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Strategy Tips for FU Words</h2>

      <p>FU is a scoring powerhouse when Z is available. FUZZY (29 pts) and FUZZ (25 pts) are elite plays. FUNKY (15 pts) uses the K tile strongly. The pair appears in -FUL words (USEFUL, CAREFUL, PAINFUL) for reliable suffixed plays. FUN (6 pts) and FUR (6 pts) clear tiles when needed.</p>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">FURZY</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">20 pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">FUZZ</span><span class="text-blue-400 text-xs">25 pts</span></span>
